*openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.068.3-r1 (04 Mar 2010)

  04 Mar 2010; Jeff Mitchell <funtoo@jefferai.org>
  +openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.068.3-r1.ebuild,
  +files/openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.068.3-cpu.patch: new ebuild
  Using -r1 to prevent probable conflict with expected upstream version.

*openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.067.4-r1 (01 Feb 2010)

  01 Feb 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org>
  +openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.067.4-r1.ebuild:  new ebuild with uvesafb support.

  28 Jan 2010; Peter Volkov <pva@gentoo.org>
  -files/openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.064.7-cifs-buildfix.patch,
