  Version bump. Dropped old. amd64/x86 stable, bug #198632.

  15 Jan 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org>
  +openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.066.10-r1.ebuild: back-ported uvesafb support into
  this kernel for much faster console and VESA video.

  15 Jan 2010; Daniel Robbins <drobbins@funtoo.org>
  openvz-sources-2.6.18.028.066.10.ebuild: added default configs.

*openvz-sources-2.6.27.3.1 (09 Jan 2010)

